1 M GROUP LUXURY REAL ESTATE LLC

data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Upgraded 4 Bedroom 2 Bathroom home + Screened & Covered Porch + Fenced in Backyard with 1,700+ square feet of living space in Avalon Park. AC with REME HALO air purifier 2017. New Water Heater Eco Friendly Hybrid 2017. The remodeled kitchen includes two toned granite countertops on main counters and island, backsplash, recessed lighting, sink and faucet, along with black appliances. The primary bedroom has a mini split AC system (2020) and a large walk in closet. The primary bathroom has been completed remodeled with a custom dual vanity and an oversized walk in double shower with seating tiled floor to ceiling! The bonus room has doors added making it a large 4th bedroom space. Down the hallway is the second full bathroom upgraded with granite countertops and hotel shower rod. The other two bedrooms are at the end of the hall. The fully screened in and covered back porch features tile flooring, a wall mounted TV and hot tub! The backyard if fully fenced in with white vinyl with a gate to the driveway. Avalon Park is a community with very desirable school zones. Community amenities include basketball courts, tennis courts, racquetball courts, playgrounds, sand volleyball court, splash pad, baseball and soccer fields, community center, walking and biking trails. HOA FEES INCLUDE CABLE & INTERNET. This house is move in ready, make an appointment to see this home today!
